				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">My rant for the day is about people who go around buying the cheap items in the bazaar only to price jack them up and sell it much higher.
<br />

<br />
Sure its a way to make money I suppose, but kind of ticks you off when you are about to go buy the cheap item you need for yourself only to see it gone and being sold by another person at a much higher price.
<br />

<br />
Yes I know this goes on because I have had people buy from me and do the same thing.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
