			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">It's all supply and demand.
<br />

<br />
I sell for the price I think is right. If you don't like my price, because it is lower than your price for the same item, then you have three options:
<br />
1. You can lower your price and match mine.
<br />
2. You can lower your price below my price and sell for cheaper than me.
<br />
3. You can buy my item/s and resell them at your price.
<br />

<br />
When I am looking to buy something, if I don't like the price, then I don't buy it. Simple as that. &lt;shrug&gt;<br />_________________<br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Whiptail "Mr Whippy" Warclaw.</span>
<br />
Iksar Primalist of <span style="font-weight: bold">53</span> seasons and <span style="font-weight: bold">0</span> AA's.
<br />
Waywatchers of Norrath.
<br />
